  <div class="topic">
    <h4>CSS Frameworks</h4>
    <p>CSS Frameworks are basically a bunch of CSS someone else has written to streamline the process of building web pages. One of the most popular frameworks is <a href="http://getbootstrap.com/" target="_blank">Boostrap</a>. Bootstrap is very large and provides many features (style and design included) but one of the most saught after features of Bootstrap (and frameworks like it) is it's layout.</p>

    <p>As we've seen, one of the hardest parts of building web pages is messing with layout. Today, we will tackle this problem head-first by building our own framework.</p>
