  <div class="topic">
    <h4>Shoestrap!</h4>
    <p>Remember when we made those columns last week in our Secret Tel Aviv project and we had to add all the tricky CSS to do this floats? Let's build that CSS in such a way that it's reusable. To do this, we'll base our framework on a 12 column, responsive grid. In the end, it will be a beautiful blank canvas like this:</p>

